nfig.php: This option will create config.php and allow you to download the complete file onto your computer. Once downloaded you will need to upload the file to the root of your XMB directory&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ol&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;select size=\"1\" name=\"method\"&gt; &lt;option value=\"1\"&gt;1)&amp;nbsp; Show the configuration on screen&lt;/option&gt; &lt;option value=\"2\"&gt;2)&amp;nbsp; Attempt to create config.php for me.&lt;/option&gt; &lt;option value=\"3\"&gt;3)&amp;nbsp; Download config.php onto my computer&lt;/option&gt; &lt;/select&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr class=\"category\"&gt; &lt;td colspan=\"2\"&gt;Database Connection Settings&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Database Name&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;Name of your database&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;input type=\"text\" name=\"db_name\" size=\"40\" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Database Username&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;User used to access database&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;input type=\"text\" name=\"db_user\" size=\"40\" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Database Password&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;Password for the Database User&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;input type=\"password\" name=\"db_pw\" size=\"40\" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Database Host&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;Database host location, usually \"localhost\"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;input type=\"text\" name=\"db_host\" size=\"40\" value=\"localhost\" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Database Type&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;The type of database server run. At this time, only mysql is supported&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;?php echo $types?&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Database Table Prefix&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;Specify a prefix for this board's database tables.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;input type=\"text\" name=\"table_pre\" size=\"40\" value=\"xmb_\" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr class=\"category\"&gt; &lt;td colspan=\"2\"&gt;Forum Settings&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Full URL&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;Put the full URL of your boards here, without any file names. Be sure to include a slash at the end.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;input type=\"text\" name=\"fullurl\" size=\"40\" value=\"&lt;?php echo 'http://'.$_SERVER['HTTP_HOST'].substr($_SERVER['PHP_SELF'], 0, strrpos($_SERVER['PHP_SELF'], '/')-7);?&gt;\" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Maximum Attachment Size&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;Enter the maximum allowed attachment size for your board here. (250*1024) for example, would be 250KB&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;input name=\"maxattachsize\" size=\"40\" value=\"(250*1024)\" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Comment Output&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;This setting will allow you to chose whether you want comments indicating templates. Default: Off&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"c_output\" value=\"TRUE\" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Restrict User Registration Per IP&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;This will restrict registration of users to one per IP address every 24 hours. Default: On&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"ip_reg\" value=\"on\" checked=\"checked\" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;IP Validation Check&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;This will check users' IP addresses are valid IPv4 or IPv6 type, if none of these. Default: Off&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"ip_check\" value=\"off\" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt;Allow Special Queries&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;This specifies whether special database queries such as USE database and SHOW database are allowed. Default: off&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"allowspecialq\" value=\"off\" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&